The '''New Republic Fleet Academy''' or '''New Republic Space Academy''' was the training institution for officers entering the [[New Republic Defense Fleet/Legends|New Republic Defense Fleet]]. It was based on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]], though other branches were eventually established on other worlds. ''[[Fleet Tactics and Combat Methodology]]'' was taught there.

While in [[Yevetha]]n captivity with [[Commodore/Legends|Commodore]] [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]], [[Lieutenant/Legends|Lieutenant]] [[Barth]] stated that by the time he had entered the Fleet Academy, it had dropped its three-language requirement. It is unclear when this occurred, but it is possible such a requirement was removed after heavy personnel losses sustained during the [[Thrawn campaign|Thrawn Crisis]] and [[Operation Shadow Hand]].

[[Ssyrmik]], [[Shreel]], and [[Marcopius]] were graduates.

